  "texts": [
    "Algorithm 6 (the Stenosis Percentage Prediction Algorithm) uses a modified version of the Swin3D 27 architecture, a state-of-the-art video classification transformer model, adapted for regression tasks to output stenoses percentages ranging between 0 to 100%.",
    "We introduce DeepCoro, a state-of-the-art pipeline for interpreting CAG videos, benchmarked against the clinical gold standard of visual assessment of stenoses by experts.",
    "Our main objective was to describe the accuracy of DeepCoro benchmarked to these human interpretations.",
    "Additionally, we compared DeepCoro's capabilities with CathAI, setting both against the benchmark of expert human analysis to underline the efficacy and advancement of our approach over current state-of-the-art approach, CathAI.",
    "To assess the efficacy of the DeepCoro pipeline, we evaluated the performance of its component algorithms (Algorithms 3-6) as well as our PCI removal algorithm."
  ],
